author: The Critical Drinker
description:
Well, The Last Of Us Season 2 is finally here. Let's see if it has the guts to stay the course and hit a hole-in-one, or if its left firmly in the sand trap. It was also a week when Katy Perry went into space for some reason, and Amazon's long-threatened Tomb Raider show seems to have bitten the dust. Join me, MauLer, Count Dankula, Echo Chamberlain and Darkhour for Open Bar 138. 

Want to support independent short films? Check out our Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/trialbyfiredrake/trial-by-fire-1
title: Open Bar #138 - Last Of Us S2, Bimbos In Space, Tomb Raider Show Cancelled
